Speaker%2C%20Telangana%20Minister%20Says...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20protest%20over%20the%20appointment%20of%20All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen's%20Akbaruddin%20Owaisi%20as%20a%20pro-tem%20Speaker%20of%20the%20assembly%2C%20Telangana%20Minister%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%20on%20Saturday%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20normal%20procedure%20and%20added%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20did%20what%20was%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGoing%20by%20seniority%20in%20Assembly%2C%20I%20should%20have%20been%20the%20pro-tem%20Speaker%2C%20the%20senior%20most%20MLA%20in%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20but%20since%20I%20have%20taken%20an%20oath%20as%20a%20minister%2C%20the%20procedure%20didn't%20allow%20me%20to%20be%20a%20pro-tem%20Speaker.%20So%20then%20we%20looked%20at%20other%206-term%20MLAs%2C%20the%20most%20senior%20MLAs.%20Akbaruddin%20Owaisi%20is%20the%20most%20senior%20MLA%20among%20all%20the%20parties.%20So%20it%20is%20a%20normal%20procedure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20Reddy%20defended%20the%20appointment%20of%20an%20All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(AIMIM)%20MLA%20as%20the%20pro-tem%20Speaker%2C%20stating%20it%20was%20a%20normal%20procedure%20followed%20even%20during%20the%20previous%20BRS%20government.%20He%20emphasised%20that%20the%20decision%20was%20made%20based%20on%20what%20was%20right%2C%20not%20due%20to%20any%20external%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20BRS%20government%20was%20there%20last%20time%2C%20they%20had%20an%20AIMIM%20MLA%20as%20the%20pro-tem%20Speaker.%20This%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20anything%20else.%20We%20did%20what%20was%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do.%20I%20cannot%20comment%20on%20the%20future%20equation%20with%20AIMIM.%20That's%20for%20our%20state%20leadership%20to%20discuss%20with%20everybody.%20And%20also%20for%20our%20national%20leadership%20to%20discuss%20and%20give%20us%20a%20direction%2C%26quot%3B%20Telangana%20Minister%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20objecting%20to%20the%20appointment%20of%20All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen's%20Akbaruddin%20Owaisi%20as%20a%20pro-tem%20Speaker%20of%20the%20assembly%2C%20Telangana%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20chief%20and%20Union%20minister%20G%20Kishan%20Reddy%20said%20on%20Saturday%20that%20the%20BJP%20decided%20to%20boycott%20the%20oath-taking%20event%2C%20alleging%20violation%20of%20assembly%20rules%20in%20the%20appointment%20of%20pro-tem%20Speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EG%20Kishan%20Reddy%20further%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20go%20to%20the%20Governor%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20pro-tem%20Speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBJP%20is%20against%20the%20appointment%20of%20Akbaruddin%20Owaisi%20as%20Pro-tem%20Speaker%20(of%20Telangana%20Assembly).%20This%20is%20against%20the%20tradition%20of%20appointing%20senior%20MLAs%20to%20the%20post.The%20BJP%20MLAs%20will%20boycott%20taking%20oaths%20before%20this%20pro-tem%20Speaker%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20MLAs%20will%20take%20oaths%20after%20a%20speaker%20is%20appointed.%20We%20will%20never%20ally%20with%20such%20a%20party%20(AIMIM).%20We%20will%20go%20to%20the%20governor%20on%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20accused%20the%20Congress%20government%20of%20'neglecting'%20the%20senior%20candidates%20for%20the%20post%20and%20of%20defying%20the%20existing%20tradition%20of%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20violation%20of%20assembly%20rules%20in%20the%20appointment%20of%20pro-tem%20Speaker%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20tradition%20of%20appointing%20senior%20leaders%20as%20the%20pro-tem%20speakers.%20However%2C%20they%20(Congress)%20have%20appointed%20Akbaruddin%20Owaisi%20due%20to%20their%20understanding%20with%20AIMIM.%20We%20object%20to%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20AIMIM%20MLA%20Akbaruddin%20Owaisi%20took%20oath%20as%20pro-tem%20Speaker%20of%20the%20Telangana%20Legislative%20Assembly%20in%20Raj%20Bhawan%2C%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20oath%20was%20administered%20by%20Telangana%20Governor%20Tamilisai%20Soundararajan.%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20Revanth%20Reddy%20was%20also%20present%20on%20the%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20governor%20appointed%20Akbaruddin%20Owaisi%20as%20the%20pro-tem%20speaker%20of%20the%20state%20assembly%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20session%20of%20the%20third%20Telangana%20State%20Legislative%20Assembly%20began%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pro-tem%20speaker%20serves%20a%20temporary%20role%2C%20officiating%20the%20assembly%20session%20until%20the%20newly-elected%20members%20are%20sworn%20in%20and%20a%20speaker%20is%20elected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Thursday%2C%20twelve%20MLAs%20took%20oaths%20as%20ministers%20in%20a%20fresh%20cabinet%20in%20Telangana%2C%20along%20with%20new%20Chief%20Minister%20Anumula%20Revanth%20Reddy%20in%20Hyderabad.%20Revanth%20Reddy%20became%20the%20first%20Congress%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20the%20youngest%20state%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20won%20an%20absolute%20majority%20in%20Telangana%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20winning%2064%20of%20119%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelangana%20Congress%20President%20Revanth%20Reddy%20won%20by%20a%20margin%20of%2032%2C532%20votes%20in%20Kodangal%20against%20BRS's%20Patnam%20Narender%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Telangana%20BJP%20took%20to%20'X'%20and%20criticised%20the%20new%20Congress%20government%20over%20the%20appointment%20of%20the%20AIMIM%20MLA%20as%20the%20pro-tem%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20government%20in%20Telangana%20is%20like%20a%20nose%20that%20blows%20when%20it%20sneezes.%20That%20is%20why%20Telangana%20state%20BJP%20President%20and%20Union%20Minister%20%40kishanreddybjp%20has%20expressed%2