3Bpress%20harder%26quot%3B%20in%20its%20war%20with%20Hamas%20on%20Saturday%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20United%20States%20blocked%20a%20ceasefire%20bid%20at%20the%20United%20Nations.%20Aid%20groups%20say%20Gaza%20faces%20an%20%26quot%3Bapocalyptic%26quot%3B%20humanitarian%20situation%20and%20is%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20being%20overwhelmed%20by%20disease%20and%20starvation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2017%2C700%20people%2C%20mostly%20women%20and%20children%2C%20have%20died%20in%20two%20months%20of%20fighting%20in%20the%20narrow%20strip%20of%20territory%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20figures%20from%20Gaza's%20health%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWashington%20vetoed%20a%20UN%20resolution%20that%20would%20have%20called%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20on%20Friday%2C%20a%20move%20strongly%20condemned%20by%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20and%20Hamas%2C%20as%20well%20as%20humanitarian%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20said%20in%20a%20video%20statement%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20very%20much%20appreciate%20the%20correct%20stance%20the%20US%20took%26quot%3B%20and%20vowed%20to%20%26quot%3Bcontinue%20our%20just%20war%20to%20eliminate%20Hamas%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20AFP%20journalist%20said%20thousands%20of%20Gazans%20were%20sheltering%20in%20the%20Al-Shifa%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%20City%2C%20which%20is%20no%20longer%20functioning%20and%20partly%20destroyed%20following%20an%20Israeli%20raid%20there%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20makeshift%20tents%20made%20from%20scraps%20of%20fabric%20and%20plastic%20filled%20the%20hospital's%20courtyards%20and%20garden%20amid%20collapsed%20walls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuheil%20Abu%20Dalfa%2C%2056%2C%20from%20the%20city's%20Shejaiya%20district%2C%20said%20he%20fled%20heavy%20bombardment%20by%20Israeli%20planes%20and%20tanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20madness.%20A%20shell%20hit%20the%20house%20and%20wounded%20my%2020-year-old%20son%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20fled%20to%20the%20Old%20City%2C%20everything%20was%20just%20strikes%20and%20destruction...%20we%20didn't%20know%20where%20to%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20know%20if%20they%20will%20storm%20the%20hospital%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Without%20anaesthetic'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20health%20authorities%20said%2071%20dead%20arrived%20at%20the%20Al-Aqsa%20Martyrs%20hospital%20in%20Deir%20al-Balah%20alone%20over%2024%20hours%2C%20and%2062%20at%20Nasser%20hospital%20in%20the%20southern%20city%20of%20Khan%20Yunis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20AFP%20correspondent%20in%20Nasser%20hospital%20saw%20a%20child%20on%20a%20makeshift%20stretcher%20and%20others%20waiting%20for%20care%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20while%20firefighters%20outside%20tried%20to%20douse%20a%20burning%20building%20partly%20destroyed%20by%20an%20Israeli%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlexandra%20Saieh%2C%20of%20Save%20the%20Children%2C%20spoke%20of%20%26quot%3Bmaggots%20being%20picked%20from%20wounds%20and%20children%20undergoing%20amputations%20without%20anaesthetic%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20%26quot%3Bis%20not%20just%20a%20catastrophe%2C%20it's%20apocalyptic%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Bushra%20Khalidi%20of%20Oxfam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20vowed%20to%20eradicate%20Hamas%20after%20its%20unprecedented%20attacks%20on%20October%207%2C%20when%20militants%20broke%20through%20Gaza's%20militarised%20border%2C%20killed%20about%201%2C200%20people%20and%20seized%20hostages%2C%20138%20of%20whom%20remain%20captive%2C%20according%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20army%20chief%20Herzi%20Halevi%20said%20it%20needed%20to%20%26quot%3Bpress%20harder%26quot%3B%20in%20its%20campaign%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20seeing%20more%20and%20more%20terrorists%20killed%2C%20more%20and%20more%20terrorists%20wounded%2C%20and%20in%20recent%20days%20we're%20seeing%20terrorists%20surrendering%20--%20this%20is%20a%20sign%20their%20network's%20falling%20apart%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20a%20ceremony%20in%20Jerusalem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20some%20Israelis%20held%20a%20pro-peace%20demonstration%2C%20while%20others%20staged%20a%20performance%20calling%20for%20the%20hostages%20to%20be%20brought%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Into%20the%20abyss'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUN%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20called%20a%20rare%20Security%20Council%20vote%20on%20a%20ceasefire%20on%20Friday%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3Bthe%20people%20of%20Gaza%20are%20looking%20into%20the%20abyss%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20vetoed%20by%20the%20US%2C%20whose%20envoy%20Robert%20Wood%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bdivorced%20from%20reality%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bwould%20leave%20Hamas%20in%20place%2C%20able%20to%20repeat%20what%20it%20did%20on%20October%207%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Foreign%20Minister%20Eli%20Cohen%20said%20a%20ceasefire%20would%20save%20Hamas%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20is%20committing%20war%20crimes%20and%20crimes%20against%20humanity%2C%20and%20would%20enable%20it%20to%20continue%20ruling%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPalestinian%20president%20Mahmud%20Abbas%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bholds%20the%20United%20States%20responsible%20for%20the%20bloodshed%20of%20Palestinian%20children%2C%20women%20and%20elderly%20people%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20veto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAvril%20Benoit%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Doctors%20Without%20Borders%20(MSF)%20charity%2C%20described%20the%20US%20veto%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsharp%20contrast%20to%20the%20values%20it%20professes%20to%20uphold%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20anger%2C%20too%2C%20in%20a%20residential%20area%20of%20Rafah%20decimated%20by%20an%20Israeli%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20resolution%20did%20the%20Security%20Council%20ever%20approve%20and%20was%20implemented%20for%20our%20cause%20and%20Palestinian%20people%3F%26quot%3B%20local%20resident%20Mohammed%20al-Khatib%20said%20amid%20the%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%2C%20which%20backs%20Hamas%2C%20warned%20it%20could%20lead%20to%20an%20%26quot%3Buncontrollable%20explosion%20in%20the%20situation%20of%20the%20region%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20Turkish%20President%20Recep%20Tayyip%20Erdogan%20denounced%20the%20UN%20body%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BIsrael%20protection%20council%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHostage%20killed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20estimated%201.9%20million%20of%20Gaza's%202.4%20million%20people%20have%20been%20displaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlocked%20from%20leaving%20the%20narrow%20territory%2C%20they%20have%20turned%20Rafah%20near%20the%20crossing%20with%20Egypt%20into%20a%20vast%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20army%20says%20it%20has%20lost%2093%20soldiers%20in%20the%20campaign%2C%20with%20two%20others%20injured%20in%20a%20failed%20bid%20to%20rescue%20hostages%20on%20Thursday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20said%20a%20hostage%2C%2025-year-old%20Sahar%20Baruch%2C%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20operation%2C%20later%20confirmed%20by%20his%20kibbutz%20community%20in%20Beeri%2C%20one%20of%20the%20worst-hit%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20air%2C%20naval%20and%20ground%20combat%20continuing%2C%20the%20military%20said%20troops%20found%20weapons%20in%20a%20school%20in%20Gaza%20City%20and%20were%20fired%20upon%20from%20an%20UN%20agency%20school%20and%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas's%20armed%20wing%20said%20it%20fired%20rockets%20towards%20Reim%20in%20southern%20Israel%20--%20the%20site%20of%20the%20Supernova%20music%20festival%20where%20364%20people%20were%20killed%20on%20October%207%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20fears%20of%20a%20wider%20regional%20conflict%2C%20with%20regular%20exchanges%20between%20Israel%20and%20Lebanon's%20Iran-backed%20Hezbollah%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20