20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20India%20has%20put%20up%20with%20%26quot%3Bunfair%20competition%26quot%3B%20for%20too%20long%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20globalisation%20era.%20He%20said%20that%20India%20must%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20call%20it%20out%20if%20the%20competition%20is%20unfair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20speaking%20at%20the%2096th%20Annual%20General%20Meeting%20(AGM)%20of%20the%20Federation%20of%20Indian%20Chambers%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20(FICCI)%20on%20Friday%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20noted%20that%20history%20is%20on%20India's%20side%20and%20every%20measurable%20index%20is%20working%20in%20India's%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20us%20a%20challenge%20both%20at%20home%20and%20abroad%2C%20is%20really%20the%20protection%20from%20unfair%20competition.%20That%20how%20do%20we%20get%20the%20data%2C%20how%20do%20we%20build%20the%20understanding%2C%20how%20do%20we%20make%20sure%20that%20feeds%20into%20policies%3F%20How%20then%20do%20we%20build%20our%20defences%3F%20And%20how%20do%20we%20take%20action%20against%20unfair%20competition%20because%20for%20too%20long%20this%20country%20(India)%20has%20put%20up%20with%20unfair%20competition%20in%20the%20name%20of%20there's%20a%20globalization%20era%2C%20aisa%20hi%20hota%20hai%2C%20we%20have%20to%20live%20with%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20have%20to%20live%20with%20it.%20If%20competition%20is%20unfair%2C%20we%20must%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20call%20it%20out%20and%20finally%2C%20how%20do%20we%20help%20with%20the%20globalization%20of%20India%20because%20the%20world%20is%20globalising.%20History%20is%20on%20our%20side.%20Every%20measurable%20index%20is%20working%20in%20our%20favour.%20In%20that%2025%20years%2C%20that%2025%20years%20is%20not%20just%20about%20growing%20in%20India%20as%20a%20Viksit%20Bharat.%20It%20is%20actually%20also%20growing%20in%20the%20world%20as%20a%20Viksit%20Bharat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20how%20the%20position%20of%20India%20in%20the%20world%20has%20changed%20over%20time%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%2015%20years%20back%2C%20India%20was%20called%20the%20back%20office%20of%20the%20world.%20However%2C%20he%20added%20that%20today%20India%20is%20called%20the%20%26quot%3Bpharmacy%20of%20the%20world%2C%20designer%20of%20the%20world%20and%20producer%20of%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20perhaps%20about%2015%20years%20ago%2C%20we%20used%20to%20be%20called%20the%20back%20office%20of%20the%20world.%20Today%2C%20we%20are%20called%20the%20pharmacy%20of%20the%20world.%20We%20are%20called%20the%20designer%20of%20the%20world.%20We%20are%20called%20the%20researcher%20of%20the%20world.%20We%20are%20called%20the%20producer%20of%20the%20world.%20We%20are%20called%20the%20digital%2C%20in%20a%20sense%2C%20the%20digital%20Pioneer%2C%20if%20you%20would.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20India's%20achievements%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20speak%20about%20our%20achievements%2C%20it%20is%20something%20real%2C%20contemporary%2C%20and%20impactful%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%20I%20take%20the%20conversation%20on%20subjects%20like%20vaccine%2C%20the%20medicines%20we%20provided%2C%20the%205G%20stack%20that%20we%20are%20rolling%20out%2C%20the%20UPI%20payments%2C%20which%20dwarf%20every%20other%20competitive%20source%20out%20there%2C%20the%20Tejas%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20just%20flown%20in.%20So%20we%20strive%20for%20food%20security%2C%20for%20energy%20security.%20These%20are%20long-standing%20problems%2C%20but%20for%20which%20we%20need%20to%20find%20better%20and%20better%20solutions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20India%20needs%20to%20make%20efforts%20as%20the%20country%20moves%20into%20the%20next%2025%20years.%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BBut%20what%20I%20can%20say%20is%2C%20as%20we%20move%20into%20the%20next%2025%20years%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20a%20challenge%20like%20EV%20or%20a%20challenge%20like%20AI.%20This%20country%20needs%20to%20pull%20up%20its%20socks.%20Get%20ready.%20I%20think%20this%20decade%20has%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPrime%20Minister%20once%20sort%20of%2C%20he%20has%20a%20turn%20of%20phrase.%20So%20he%20said%20it's%20both%20about%20tradition%20and%20technology.%20How%20do%20we%20get%20it%20both%20together%3F%20I%20think%20in%20a%20way%2C%20for%20us%20today%2C%20it's%20also%20both%20about%20being%20more%20nationalist%20and%20being%20internationalist.%20How%20do%20we%2C%20again%2C%20find%20the%20balance%3F%20How%20do%20we%20reconcile%20both%20together%3F%20And%20what%20I%20can%20say%20is%20that%20it%20is%20only%20through%20continuous%20progress%20today%20that%20we%20can%20really%20lay%20the%20basis%20for%20greatness%20tomorrow.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20remarks%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20also%20explained%20his%20perspective%20on%20'Bharat'%20and%20asserted%20that%20Bharat%20is%20a%20'belief'%20and%20'attitude'%20rather%20than%20just%20a%20geographical%20entity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20me%2C%20Bharat%20is%20actually%20a%20belief%20and%20an%20attitude.%20For%20me%2C%20Bharat%20has%20an%20economic%20dimension.%20It%20has%20a%20political%20meaning.%20It%20has%20cultural%2C%20social%2C%20I%20would%20say%20even%20personal%20expressions.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20the%20term%2C%20Bharat%20means%20don't%20let%20other%20people%20define%20you.%20Try%20and%20define%20yourself.%20That%20it%20has%20to%20come%20from%20itself%20because%20that%20very%20term%20Bharat%20which%20is%20so%20laden%20with%20symbolism%20actually%20captures%20centuries%20of%20what%20we%20are%20all%20about%20as%20a%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20fro