herapy%20for%20sickle%20cell%20anemia.%3Cp%3EMeletios%20Verras%2F%20iStock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20FDA%20approved%20the%20first%20gene%20therapies%20for%20sickle%20cell%20anemia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20two%20approved%20treatments%2C%20Casgevy%20and%20Lyfgenia%2C%20will%20cost%20%242.2%20million%20and%20%243.1%20million.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECasgevy%20is%20the%20first%20therapy%20to%20use%20the%20CRISPR%20gene%20editing%20tool%20that%20won%20the%20Nobel%20Prize.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FDA%20approved%20the%20first%20gene%20therapy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fmaintaining-hold-on-bluebird-bio-weighing-lyfgenia-s-fda-approval-against-market-challenges-and-competition-1032887148%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etreatments%20for%20sickle%20cell%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Friday%2C%20but%20it%20will%20cost%20patients%20millions%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20approved%20therapies%2C%20developed%20by%20Vertex%20Pharmaceuticals%20and%20called%20Casgevy%2C%20is%20the%20first%20of%20its%20kind%20to%20use%20the%20CRISPR%20gene-editing%20tool%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fnews-events%2Fpress-announcements%2Ffda-approves-first-gene-therapies-treat-patients-sickle-cell-disease%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFDA%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmmanuelle%20Charpentier%20and%20Jennifer%20A.%20Doudna%20won%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unesco.org%2Fen%2Farticles%2Fjennifer-doudna-and-emmanuelle-charpentier-win-2020-nobel-prize-chemistry%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENobel%20Prize%20in%20chemistry%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202020%20for%20their%20work%20creating%20the%20CRISPR%20tool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESickle%20cell%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fnew-york-jets-tevin-coleman-raising-daughter-with-sickle-cell-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20inherited%20blood%20d