20with%20Smita%20Prakash%2C%20Gambhir%20talked%20about%20how%20the%20media%20always%20showed%20his%20fight%20with%20Shahid%20Afridi%20before%20every%20'India%20vs%20Pakistan'%20match.%20The%20former%20player%20also%20asked%20them%20to%20show%20something%20positive%20like%20the%20Men%20in%20Blue's%20win%20against%20the%20%26quot%3BMen%20in%20Green'%20in%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20there's%20a%20match%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20why%20do%20they%20always%20show%20my%20fight%20with%20Shahid%20Afridi%2C%20there%20are%20so%20many%20other%20fights%20that%20have%20happened.%20Show%20something%20positive.%20Show%20when%20India%20has%20won%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20against%20Pakistan%2C%26quot%3B%20Gambhir%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201984%2C%20India%20won%20their%20maiden%20Asia%20Cup%20title%20after%20they%20defeated%20Pakistan%20by%2054%20runs%20at%20the%20Sharjah%20Cricket%20Stadium%20to%20win%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGautam%20Gambhir%20and%20Shahid%20Afridi%20have%20had%20a%20history%20of%20on-field%20rivalry.%20In%202009%2C%20the%20two%20fought%20during%20an%20ODI%20in%20Kanpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20they%20renewed%20their%20rivalry%20in%20the%20opening%20match%20of%20the%20Legends%20League%20Cricket%20(LLC).%20Gambhir%20captained%20India%20Maharajas%2C%20while%20Afridi%20led%20Asia%20Lions.%20During%20the%20match%2C%20Gambhir%20was%20hit%20while%20batting.%20Afridi%20checked%20on%20Gambhir%20and%20asked%20if%20he%20was%20okay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20moments%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%20Gambhir%20and%20Afridi%20have%20also%20had%20a%20war%20of%20words.%20Gambhir%20once%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAfridi%20has%20only%20grown%20in%20age%2C%20mentally%20he%20is%20still%2016.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGambhir%20further%20lambasted%20the%20media%20for%20always%20running%20behind%20numbers.%20He%20added%20that%20everything%20is%20not%20about%20TRP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%2C%20it's%20a%20game%20of%20numbers%2C%20right%3F%20In%20the%20end%2C%20how%20much%20traction%20you're%20getting%20on%20social%20media%2C%20it's%20not%20all%20about%20TRP.%20If%20you%20keep%20showing%20one%20thing%20then%20it%20gets%20negative.%20There%20are%20many%20other%20positive%20things%20to%20show%20as%20well%2C%20India%20has%20defeated%20Pakistan%20in%20many%20important%20matches%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20his%20brawl%20with%20Afridi%2C%20the%2042-year-old%20said%20that%20he%20moved%20on%20from%20it%20a%20long%20back%20and%20if%20they%20want%20to%20stick%20to%20it%20then%20the%20former%20player%20is%20completely%20fine%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGambhir%20added%20that%20he%20could%20not%20control%20the%20broadcaster%2C%20what%20he%20could%20do%20is%20to%20win%20all%20the%20games%20and%20be%20passionate%20towards%20his%20team%20or%20franchise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20move%20on%20then%20absolutely%20fine%20with%20it%2C%20because%20I%20have%20moved%20on%20a%20long%20back.%20How%20can%20I%20control%20what%20a%20broadcaster%20wants%20to%20show%20this%20is%20not%20in%20my%20hands.%20What%20is%20in%20my%20hand%20is%20to%20win%20all%20the%20games%20and%20be%20passionate%20about%20it%20and%20be%20accountable%20of%20true%20to%20the%20franchise%20or%20team%20that%20I%20am%20representing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20ODI%20match%20in%202007%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20duo%20was%20involved%20in%20a%20fight%20after%20a%20boundary%20in%20the%2020th%20over.%20In%20the%20second%20ball%2C%20Gambhir%20was%20running%20for%20a%20single%20when%20Afridi%20came%20in%20the%20way.%20Following%20this%2C%20the%20two%20were%20involved%20in%20a%20heated%20exchange%20but%20later%20the%20on-field%20umpires%20had%20to%20cool%20them%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702142160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Fj3a6lan8_ga