0exactly%20a%20day%20after%20he%20threw%20his%20weight%20behind%20expelled%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20following%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20parliamentary%20ethics%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20were%20warned%20many%20times%20against%20statements%20or%20actions%20against%20the%20policies%2C%20ideology%20and%20discipline%20of%20the%20party.%20But%2C%20despite%20that%20you%20have%20continuously%20been%20acting%20against%20the%20party%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20BSP%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%202018%2C%20you%20were%20working%20with%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda%20of%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20party.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20both%20the%20BSP%20and%20JD(S)%20were%20contesting%20together%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20assembly%20election.%20After%20the%20Karnataka%20election%2C%20you%20were%20given%20a%20ticket%20from%20Amroha%20and%20asked%20to%20contest%20from%20there%20due%20to%20Deve%20Gowda%E2%80%99s%20insistence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20then%20went%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CDeve%20Gowda%20had%20even%20said%20that%20you%20would%20be%20contesting%20the%20Amroha%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20you%20will%20be%20working%20for%20the%20BSP.%20However%2C%20despite%20winning%20from%20Amroha%2C%20you%20have%20forgotten%20all%20the%20promises%20and%20assurances%20you%20made%20and%20indulged%20in%20anti-party%20activities.%20The%20party%20has%20decided%20to%20suspend%20you%20with%20immediate%20effect.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20December%208%2C%20Ali%20had%20held%20a%20one-man%20protest%20outside%20parliament%20against%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20expulsion.%20He%20hung%20a%20placard%20around%20his%20neck%20on%20which%20it%20was%20written%20%E2%80%9Cdon%E2%80%99t%20turn%20(the)%20victim%20into%20(the)%20culprit%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20put%20this%20(poster)%20because%20the%20committee%20also%20mentioned%20me%20in%20its%20recommendation%E2%80%A6%20because%20I%20want%20to%20bring%20her%20justice.%20She%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20given%20an%20opportunity%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20Ali%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahua-moitra-expelled-lok-sabha-danish-ali-ramesh-bidhuri-honour-died-when-ramesh-bidhuri-danish-ali-on-mahua-moitra-expulsion-4645867%5C%22%3Ehad%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20one%20side%2C%20the%20whole%20world%20saw%20how%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20(a%20BJP%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP)%20acted%E2%80%A6%20was%20there%20no%20sense%20of%20honour%20or%20decorum%20in%20Parliament%20then%3F%20Why%20now%3F%20What%20is%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%20a%20furious%20Ali%20had%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20his%20suspension%2C%20Ali%20said%20that%20he%20is%20ready%20to%20face%20consequences%20by%20opposing%20the%20%E2%80%9Canti-people%20policies%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20In%20a%20series%20of%20posts%20on%20X%20(formerly%2C%20Twitter)%2C%20he%20wrote%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cspan%3EI%20will%20always%20be%20grateful%20to%20sister%20Mayawati%3Cem%3E%20ji%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20she%20helped%20me%20become%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20by%20giving%20me%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBSP%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eticket.%20Sister%20also%20made%20me%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20BSP%20parliamentary%20party.%20I%20always%20received%20her%20immense%20love%20and%20support.%20Her%20decision%20today%20is%20unfortunate.%20I%20worked%20hard%20%3Cspan%3Eto%20strengthen%20BSP%20and%20have%20never%20done%20any%20kind%20of%20anti-party%20work.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20people%20of%20Amroha%20are%20witness%20to%20this.%20I%20have%20opposed%20the%20anti-people%20policies%20of%20the%20BJP%20%3C%2Fspan%3Egovernment%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20so.%20The%20public%E2%80%99s%20wealth%20is%20owned%20by%20a%20few%20capitalists%20and%20have%20raised%20my%20voice%20against%20looting%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20so.%20Because%20this%20is%20true%20public%20service.%20If%20doing%20this%20is%20a%20crime%2C%20then%20I%20have%20committed%20this%20crime%2C%20and%20I%20am%20ready%20to%20face%20the%20punishment%20for%20it.%20I%20want%20to%20assure%20the%20people%20of%20Amroha%20that%20I%20will%20always%20be%20at%20your%20service.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%88%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%B6%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%97%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%BC%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%82%E0%A4%81%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%89%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%9D%E0%A5%87%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbspindia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40bspindia%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%9F%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%9F%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AD%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%A6%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%E0%A5%A4%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%9D%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%AF%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B2%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%AD%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%E0%A5%A4%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%9D%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%88%E0%A4%B5%20%E0%A4%89%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%AE%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%