illion%20(8%20crore)%20FTVs%20in%202019%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-polls-bjp-congress-drives-register-first-time-voters-8557773.html%5C%22%3Eestimates%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%202024%20are%20150%20million%2C%20or%2015%20crore.%20That%20is%20an%20almost%20two-fold%20increase%20between%20the%20two%20elections.%20Even%20if%20we%20discount%20the%202024%20estimates%20by%2025%25%2C%20FTVs%20will%20form%20a%20sizeable%20proportion%20of%20total%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFTVs%20comprise%20between%2010-15%25%20of%20the%20total%20electorate%2C%20perhaps%20more%20than%20most%20castes%20or%20religious%20denominations.%20They%20constitute%20a%20separate%20and%20distinct%20cohort%2C%20with%20their%20own%20problems%2C%20aspirations%2C%20preferences%20and%20mental%20make-up.%20You%20would%20expect%20that%20all%20major%20political%20parties%20would%20be%20aware%20of%20this%20and%20that%20they%20would%20cater%20to%20them%20specifically%20in%20their%20manifestos%2C%20as%20they%20do%20for%20all%20other%20electorally%20significant%20blocs.%20Especially%20as%20available%20data%20shows%20that%20FTVs%20have%20a%20significant%20influence%20and%20impact%20on%20election%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%202014%20analysis%20by%20IndiaSpend%20concluded%20that%20this%20youthful%20segment%20had%20catapulted%20the%20BJP%20to%20power%20in%20the%20five%20states%20with%20the%20highest%20proportion%20of%20young%20voters.%20Below%20is%20a%20table%20indicating%20the%20five%20states%20which%20had%20added%20the%20most%20FTVs%20between%202014%20and%202018%2C%20and%20the%20number%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20each%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%20border%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20cellspacing%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20data-sheets-root%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20cellpadding%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ccolgroup%3E%5Cn%3Ccol%20width%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ccol%20width%3D%5C%22180%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ccol%20width%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fcolgroup%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5