E2%80%99s%20brand%20equity%20is%20no%20longer%20as%20strong%20as%20it%20was%20in%202018-19%2C%20that%20the%20appeal%20of%20Hindutva%20has%20peaked%2C%20and%20that%20economic%20issues%20such%20as%20price%20rise%20and%20unemployment%20have%20begun%20to%20bite.%20What%20then%20is%20the%20generic%20explanation%20for%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20phenomenal%20rise%20in%20vote%20share%20in%202023%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20distinct%20possibility%20that%20the%20answer%20could%20lie%20in%20the%20hitherto%20ignored%20FTV.%20An%20interesting%20article%20in%20the%20New%20Indian%20Expressed%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fopinions%2F2023%2Fnov%2F25%2Fthe-seven-sins-of-new-india-2635919.html%5C%22%3EThe%20Seven%20Sins%20of%20New%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%20by%20K.%20Jayakumar%2C%20published%20on%20November%2025%2C%20postulates%20that%20the%20young%20generation%20of%20today%20(read%20FTV)%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwith%20no%20exposure%20to%20an%20earlier%20ethos%20of%20public%20life%2C%20begins%20to%20believe%20that%20what%20it%20sees%20today%20is%20normal.%E2%80%9D%20And%20what%20this%20generation%20sees%20today%20is%20listed%20by%20Jayakumar%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cseven%20sins%20of%20new%20India.%E2%80%9D%20These%20are%3A%20Inequality%20before%20the%20law%2C%20vindictive%20vehemence%2C%20intolerance%20to%20criticism%2C%20corruption%2C%20doublespeak%2C%20window%20dressing%2C%20and%20the%20baggage%20of%20secularism.%20These%20seven%20sins%20comprise%20the%20new%20normal%20and%20have%20changed%20the%20idiom%20of%20public%20life%20and%20polity%20completely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20find%20this%20a%20fascinating%20thesis%2C%20one%20which%20makes%20eminent%20sense.%20Just%20step%20back%20and%20consider%3A%20the%20FTV%20of%20today%20was%20only%20eight%20years%20old%20in%202014%2C%20and%20thirteen%20in%202019.%20These%20are%20impressionable%20ages%2C%20the%20crucible%20when%20values%2C%20behaviour%2C%20beliefs%20and%20prejudices%20are%20formed.%20This%20generation%20has%20grown%20up%20in%20the%20Modi%20years%20and%20has%20seen%20nothing%20but%20the%20seven%20deadly%20sins%20in%20operation%2C%20carpet-bombed%20by%20media%20and%20party%20propaganda%20to%20believe%20in%20this%20right-wing%20ideology%20and%20that%20Modi%20is%20the%20Vishwaguru.%20They%20are%20creatures%20of%20this%20new%20toxic%20environment%2C%20and%20their%20value%20systems%20can%20only%20align%20with%20this%20new%20reality%2C%20having%20experienced%20no%20other%20one.%20I%2C%20for%20one%2C%20therefore%20would%20be%20very%20surprised%20if%20they%20did%20not%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20elections%2C%20almost%20as%20a%20bloc.%20This%20thesis%20brings%20together%20all%20the%20anecdotal%20data%20and%20statistics%20mentioned%20above%2C%20and%20may%20go%20some%20way%20in%20explaining%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20continued%20appeal%20and%20the%20increase%20in%20its%20vote%20share.%20The%20FTV%20may%20not%20be%20the%20only%20explanation%20but%20it%20certainly%20merits%20a%20serious%20look.%20And%20the%20beauty%20of%20this%20phenomenon%20is%20that%20with%20each%20incremental%20year%20of%20this%20regime%2C%20their%20numbers%20will%20keep%20increasing%20by%20a%20few%20millions%2C%20providing%20the%20BJP%20with%20an%20ever-increasing%20constituency%20of%20programmed%20supporters.%20There%20can%20be%20no%20worse%20news%20for%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20may%20be%20wrong%20(I%20usually%20am%20in%20such%20matters)%2C%20but%20can%20the%20opposition%20continue%20to%20ignore%20the%20FTV%3F%20They%20may%20be%20their%20ticket%20to%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Favayshukla.blogspot.com%2F2023%2F12%2Fis-first-time-voter-x-factor-in-bjps.html%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20the%20author%E2%80%99s%20blog%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Favayshukla.blogspot.com%2F%5C%22%3EView%20from%20%5BGreater%5D%20Kailash%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20lightly