en%20he%20objected%20to%20being%20asked%20to%20the%20clean%20the%20personal%20toilet%20of%20the%20VC%20at%20his%20personal%20residence%20in%20Pune%2C%20his%20services%20were%20terminated.%20What%20is%20particularly%20alarming%20in%20this%20case%20is%20that%20the%20driver%20belongs%20to%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%E2%80%A6%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20practice%20violates%20the%20principles%20of%20equality%20and%20justice%20enshrined%20in%20our%20Constitution.%20The%20concerned%20VC%20claims%20to%20be%20a%20teacher%20of%20constitutional%20law%20teacher%20and%20yet%20his%20actions%20go%20against%20the%20very%20ethos%20of%20what%20he%20preaches.%20Such%20a%20practice%20is%20also%20indicative%20of%20a%20form%20of%20modern%20slavery%20where%20individuals%20are%20coerced%20into%20performing%20tasks%20outside%20the%20scope%20of%20their%20employment%2C%20violating%20their%20dignity%20and%20perpetuating%20a%20system%20of%20discrimination%20based%20on%20caste%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20humbly%20request%20your%20institution%20to%20investigate%20this%20matter%20thoroughly%E2%80%A6the%20students%20will%20ensure%20that%20all%20the%20victims%20will%20come%20and%20give%20evidence%2C%20if%20required%E2%80%A6There%20are%20an%20estimated%2018.3%20million%20people%20in%20India%20forced%20into%20forms%20of%20modern%20slavery%20(about%2039%25%20of%20the%20world%20average).%20No%20NLU%20should%20be%20a%20forum%20where%20such%20practices%20carry%20on%20unchecked%E2%80%A6We%20end%20with%20the%20words%20of%20Martin%20Luther%20King%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EInjustice%20Anywhere%20Is%20a%20Threat%20To%20Justice%20Everywhere.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWrite%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eombudsperson%40thewire.in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702111512000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F03190918%2FScreenshot-2022-02-03-at