2C%20Argentina%2C%20began%20with%20his%20voice%20announcing%20across%20a%20darkened%20stage%20and%20stadium%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20out%20of%20consideration%20for%20your%20fellow%20patrons%2C%20please%20turn%20off%20your%20cell%20phones.%20And%20secondly%2C%20if%20you%20are%20one%20of%20those%20%E2%80%98I-love-Pink-Floyd-but-I-can%E2%80%99t-stand-Roger%E2%80%99s-politics%E2%80%99%20people%2C%20you%20might%20do%20well%20to%20f***%20off%20to%20the%20bar!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20packed%20stadium%20erupted%20in%20loud%20cheers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhere%20most%20international%20megastars%20in%20both%20movies%20and%20the%20music%20industry%20have%20refrained%20from%20speaking%20out%20against%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20military%20brutality%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Roger%20Waters%2C%20co-founder%20of%20the%20legendary%20group%2C%20Pink%20Floyd%2C%20continues%20to%20be%20an%20exception.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20nothing%20subtle%20about%20Waters%E2%80%99%20activism.%20Not%20only%20does%20the%20musician%20wear%20the%20Palestinian%20%3Cem%3Ekheffiyeh%3C%2Fem%3E%20when%20he%20performs%2C%20but%20the%20gigantic%20screens%20behind%20his%20performing%20stage%20also%20bear%20constant%20witness%20to%20his%20political%20beliefs.%20Names%20and%20photos%20of%20political%20prisoners%2C%20persecuted%20activists%2C%20slain%20journalists%2C%20and%20those%20who%20have%20died%20in%20Gaza%20scroll%20across%20the%20screens.%20And%20then%2C%20of%20course%2C%20there%20are%20the%20actual%20lyrics%20of%20his%20songs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWaters%E2%80%99%20activism%20has%2C%20naturally%2C%20come%20at%20a%20cost.%20Some%20of%20his%20recent%20shows%20nearly%20got%20cancelled%20in%20South%20America%20and%20some%20hotels%20cancelled%20his%20reservations%20with%20no%20reasons%20given.%20He%20continues%20to%20be%20called%20%E2%80%98antisemitic%E2%80%99%20by%20many%20in%20the%20mainstream%20media%20and%20elsewhere.%20Waters%E2%80%99%20response%20to%20the%20accusation%20is%20perhaps%20best%20captured%20in%20an%20open%20letter%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fcommentisfree%2F2019%2Fapr%2F17%2Fmadonna-human-rights-tel-aviv-israel-palestine%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20fellow%20musician%2C%20Madonna%2C%20in%202019%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CBecause%20I%20support%20human%20rights%20and%20criticise%20the%20Israeli%20government%20for%20its%20violations%2C%20I%20am%20routinely%20accused%20of%20being%20antisemitic.%20That%20accusation%20can%20be%20used%20as%20a%20smokescreen%20to%20divert%20attention%20and%20discredit%20those%20who%20shine%20a%20light%20on%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20crimes%20against%20humanity.%20I%20should%20point%20out%20that%20I%20support%20the%20fight%20for%20human%20rights%20for%20all%20oppressed%20peoples%20everywhere.%20The%20religion%20of%20the%20oppressor%20is%20neither%20here%20nor%20there.%20If%20I%20support%20the%20Rohingyas%20and%20deplore%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20persecution%20of%20them%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20make%20me%20anti-Buddhist.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWaters%E2%80%99%20first%20encounter%20with%20Palestine%20came%20in%202005%20when%20during%20a%20musical%20tour%20of%20Europe%2C%20his%20agent%20suggested%20that%20since%20they%20had%20a%20few%20days%20between%20gigs%2C%20they%20could%20fit%20one%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%E2%80%99s%20Hayarkon%20Park.%20Waters%20agreed%2C%20but%20almost%20immediately%20started%20getting%20appeals%20requesting%20him%20not%20to%2C%20including%20one%20from%20Omar%20Barghouti%2C%20co-founder%20of%20the%20Boycott%2C%20Divestment%20and%20Sanctions%20movement%2C%20(and%20incidentally%2C%20a%20recipient%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20Peace%20Award)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarghouti%20informed%20Waters%20that%20Hayarkon%20Park%2C%20the%20venue%20for%20the%20proposed%20concert%2C%20was%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20built%20over%20Palestinian%20graves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWaters%2C%20who%20by%20his%20own%20admission%2C%20did%20not%20know%20very%20much%20about%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20Palestinians%20at%20the%20time%2C%20agreed%20to%20shift%20the%20venue%20to%20a%20multi-faith%20agricultural%20community%2C%20called%20Neve%20Shalom%2C%20halfway%20between%20Tel%20Aviv%20and%20Jerusalem.%20The%20gig%2C%20with%2060%2C000%20people%20attending%2C%20was%20a%20success%20by%20any%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20show%2C%20Waters%20appealed%20to%20the%20Israeli%20youth%20in%20attendance%20to%20live%20in%20peace%20with%20their%20Palestinian%20neighbours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20audience%2C%20euphoric%20till%20that%20point%2C%20suddenly%20went%20very%20quiet.%20But%20it%20was%20not%20the%20quietness%20of%20acquiescence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWaters%20described%20the%20moment%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoEdNEb8_20o%3Fsi%3DEnTTyvMfhOEi0n7_%5C%22%3Ea%20recent%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20TRT%20World%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20uncanny.%20They%20went%20very%2C%20very%20quiet.%20I%20went%20back%20the%20next%20year%20and%20went%20on%20an%20extended%20tour%20%E2%80%A6%20all%20over%20the%20West%20bank%20and%20it%20was%20chilling%20beyond%20anything%20I%20could%20ever%20have%20imagined.%20The%20absolute%20disdain%20and%20disgust%20with%20which%20the%20young%20Israeli%20border%20guards%20treated%20us%2C%20including%20me%20with%20a%20British%20passport%20in%20an%20UNRWA%20vehicle!%20I%20remember%20thinking%20at%20the%20time%2C%20if%20they%E2%80%99re%20like%20that%20to%20me%2C%20what%20must%20they%20be%20like%20to%20the%20Palestinians%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20back%20in%202006.%20Today%2C%20Waters%E2%80%99%20voice%20breaks%20as%20he%20speaks%20of%20the%20continuing%20massacre%20in%20Gaza.%20%E2%80%9CI%20spend%20my%20life%20teetering%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20tears.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08141743%2Fimage-1588.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221030%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08141743%2Fimage-1588.png%201030w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08141743%2Fimage-1588-300x121.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08141743%2Fimage-1588-1024x413.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688305%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22415%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERoger%20Waters%20at%20a%20Desert%20Trip%20concert.%20Photo%3A%20YouTube%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWaters%20has%20tried%20to%20be%20the%20voice%20of%20conscience%20to%20his%20fellow%20musicians%20as%20well.%20He%20publicly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Froger-waters-calls-on-madonna-not-to-perform-at-eurovision-in-tel-aviv%2F%5C%22%3Easked%3C%2Fa%3E%20Madonna%20not%20to%20play%20at%20the%20Eurovision%20song%20contest%20finals%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReminding%20her%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20Universal%20Declaration%20of%20Human%20Rights%2C%20he%20asked%20whether%20she%20stood%20by%20them%2C%20and%20if%20she%20did%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwould%20she%20help%20her%20brothers%20and%20sisters%20in%20their%20struggle%20for%20human%20rights%20or%20would%20she%20cross%20over%20and%20walk%20on%20by%20the%20other%20side%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20say%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20of%20my%20fellow%20musicians%20who%20have%20recently%20performed%20in%20Israel%20say%20they%20are%20doing%20it%20to%20build%20bridges%20and%20further%20the%20cause%20of%20peace.%20Bullshit.%20To%20perform%20in%20Israel%20is%20a%20lucrative%20gig%20but%20to%20do%20so%20serves%20to%20normalise%20the%20occupation%2C%20the%20apartheid%2C%20the%20ethnic%20cleansing%2C%20the%20incarceration%20of%20children%2C%20the%20slaughter%20of%20unarmed%20protesters%20%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadonna%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fslate.com%2Fculture%2F2019%2F05%2Feurovision-2019-madonna-tel-aviv-israel-like-a-prayer.html%5C%22%3Ewent%20ahead%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20show%2C%20regardless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWaters%20speaks%20often%20of%20his%20father%20who%20died%20fighting%20the%20Nazis%20in%20Europe%20in%20World%20War%20II.%20Although%20he%20was%20too%20young%20at%20the%20time%20to%20have%20any%20memories%20of%20him%2C%20he%20makes%20it%20a%20point%20to%20credit%20his%20mother%20for%20teaching%20him%20how%20to%20make%20difficult%20moral%20choices.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20when%20he%20was%20still%20in%20his%20teens%20and%20struggling%20with%20a%20decision%2C%20she%20would%20suggest%20that%20the%20young%20Roger%20read%20up%20as%20much%20as%20he%20could%20on%20the%20topic%20at%20hand%2C%20educate%20himself%20thoroughly%20on%20all%20sides%20of%20the%20issue%2C%20and%20then%20do%20the%20right%20thing.%20This%20is%20advice%20that%20the%20music%20icon%20seems%20to%20be%20following%20right%20up%20to%20his%2080s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWaters%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20a%20lack%20of%20subtlety.%20But%20looking%20at%20the%20carnage%2C%20death%2C%20and%20devastation%20that%20the%20Palestinians%20are%20facing%20daily%20at%20the%20hand%20of%20the%20Israeli%20army%20and%20air%20force%2C%20perhaps%20the%20time%20for%20subtlety%20is%20now%20over.%20Perhaps%20now%20is%20the%20time%20to%20take%20a%20page%20out%20of%20Waters%E2%80%99%20book%20and%20call%20the%20situation%20in%20Gaza%20for%20what%20it%20really%20is%20%E2%80%93%20a%20genocide%20and%20war%20crime%20unlike%20any%20this%20century%20has%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Ffvrg%5C%22%3ERohit%20Kumar%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20educator%2C%20author%2C%20and%20independent%20journalist%2C%20and%20can%20be%20reached%20at%20