orts%20for%20the%20event.%20A%20circular%2C%20signed%20by%20the%20superintendent%20of%20Kurseong%20Sub-Divisional%20Hospital%20has%20been%20shared%20widely%20on%20social%20media.%20It%20has%20details%20on%20the%20medial%20team%20formed%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20VVIPs%20between%20December%204%20and%2010.%20The%20team%20includes%20specialists%20ranging%20from%20paediatricians%20to%20ophthalmologists.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20decision%20to%20divert%20medical%20resources%20and%20personnel%20for%20a%20private%20event%20has%20sparked%20criticism%20from%20opposition%20parties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBJP%20leader%20Subhendu%20Adhikari%20commented%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20like%20a%20royal%20family%20wedding.%20Government%20doctors%20have%20been%20made%20to%20serve%20the%20royals%20of%20the%20state%2C%20having%20been%20taken%20away%20from%20their%20duty%20to%20serve%20the%20commoners.%20How%20does%20it%20matter%20to%20them%20that%20people%20are%20affected%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECommunist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20leader%20Dr%20Sujan%20Chakraborty%20called%20this%20a%20gross%20abuse%20of%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20Z-category%20VIPs.%20But%20creating%20medical%20teams%20dedicated%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20her%20nephew%20for%20seven%20days%20is%20unprecedented.%20The%20chief%20minister%20arrived%20in%20north%20Bengal%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20two%20days%20after%20the%20medical%20team%E2%80%99s%20deputation.%20What%20was%20the%20team%20doing%20there%20%5Bfor%20two%20days%5D%20when%20those%20who%20needed%20its%20services%20were%20being%20denied%20treatment%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Kunal%20Ghosh%20has%20termed%20these%20allegations%20baseless.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20wedding%20ritual%20but%20is%20staying%20at%20one%20of%20the%20resorts%20booked%20for%20the%20weeding.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20pictures%20of%20plucking%20teas%20while%20wearing%20local%20dress%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20and%20were%20reported%20upon%20by%20Kolkata%20outlets%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20diversion%20of%20medical%20resources%20for%20the%20VVIP%20wedding%20in%20Kurseong%20has%20triggered%20repercussions%20for%20the%20health%20system%20in%20the%20hills%2C%20compelling%20locals%20to%20seek%20medical%20attention%20in%20distant%20towns%20like%20Siliguri%20and%20Jalpaiguri%2C%20opposition%20has%20alleged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08175956%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-12-08-at-11.58.55-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22791%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08175956%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-12-08-at-11.58.55-AM.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08175956%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-12-08-at-11.58.55-AM-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688360%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22593%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20north%20Bengal%20hospital.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20many%20doctors%2C%20nurses%2C%20and%20health%20workers%20have%20been%20moved%20for%20seven%20days%20because%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20family%20wedding%20ceremony.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20people%20who%20used%20to%20get%20services%20in%20government%20hospitals%20are%20being%20turned%20away%20and%20told%20that%20they%20should%20return%20after%20seven%20days.%20Denying%20